<br>
Taibbo <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukambic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kambic</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/17/01 8:29:36 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=529.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://kambic.homestead.com/files/gotwang.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Which PvP server is best ?</span><hr size=1> Well, whatcha lookin for?<br>
<br>
I'm enjoying SZ, but I also played to 40 on RZ. All the advice I can give you is I suggest playing on teams (tho you already want to) because it gives you a PvP motivation outside of "griefing."<br>
<br>
 <p><center><img src="http://kambic.homestead.com/files/wangenvy1.1.jpg"></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uurshulgi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Urshulgi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/18/01 3:00:21 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=529.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> sullon or rallos</span><hr size=1> VZ and TZ the team situation is extremely unbalanced at this point in the end game.  You're better off with sullon or rallos to tell you the truth. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/urhainy.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rhainy</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/18/01 7:25:08 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=529.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: sullon or rallos</span><hr size=1> Well..<br>
<br>
TZ and VZ have problems with x teaming and imortal healers, people you can't kill healing the people you can.<br>
<br>
And sullon has HUGE imbalance in teams. Evil pretty much owns everything since they're 90% of the server pop and whatver good or newts did play rerolled evil. But if you're gonna play evil, might as well play on a blue server since it's the same experence. There's no one to PK if you're evil.<br>
<br>
It's close to impossible for any non solo class to lvl up good or neutral right now since there's no one to group with...<br>
<br>
You're prolly better off on RZ actually. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=elegance>Elegance</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_thatch.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/18/01 1:16:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=529.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: sullon or rallos</span><hr size=1> @#%$ guys dont send a rogue to rallos.<br>
rallos has item loot,<br>
and a huge amount of cheaters useing showeq and various other hacks to make them selves almost untouchable.<br>
and lastly rallos has no real gm support when it comes to these people. I watched a group sit on the walls in nfp and farm PLAYERS for over 4 hours with no trouble from the guides/gms. <br>
if you want to start over on a pvp server I would suggest it be a daoc server to be honest. <p>"PvE in EQ is definately entertaining, enjoyable, and challenging."</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukambic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kambic</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/18/01 9:41:03 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=529.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://kambic.homestead.com/files/gotwang.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: sullon or rallos</span><hr size=1> In all truth, if you want to play real PvP, I suggest a Quake III Arena server =p <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ulirintz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lirin TZ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/18/01 9:58:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=529.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/ribbon_small.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: sullon or rallos</span><hr size=1> UT and CS kick Q3's ass, thxinfola~ <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=10458 >Liringlas Lookinglass</a><br>
HWW~ Bard of the 54th Song<br>Fennin Ro<br><a href=http://www.mysticalprophecy.com/>Mystical Prophecy</a>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukambic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kambic</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/18/01 11:48:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=529.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://kambic.homestead.com/files/gotwang.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: sullon or rallos</span><hr size=1> Personally enjoy the Opera mod for HL, but I don't run a very fast connection so rarely play any FPS game. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ufudly.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fudly</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/19/01 7:00:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=529.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Sullen Zek</span><hr size=1> Yes Sullen Zeks server population is low so it will be hard to find a group as a rogue but it has many other perks. <br>
#1 No stupid rules. Every other PvP server has a ton of players who do their best to break every rule possible while reporting as many as they can. This is bogus play where there are no rules.<br>
#2 Hard coded teams. Immortal healing, cross-teaming, all that bluebie stuff is just bogus.<br>
#3 6-60 range for pvp, Yes this one can get on your nerves at times but lets face it for every death you take from dieing to a high level is made up 10x over when you get to repay the favor. <br>
#4 No item loot, I'm sorry this would be cool if there were very few no drop stuff and you were allowed to loot stuff in bags but since you can't forget it, not worth the trouble.<br>
#5 20% experience bonus half exp loss on deaths. Everquest isn't considered a leveling treadmill for nothing. <br>
<br>
And for gods sake be Good or Neutral. There are evil guilds capable of raiding planes that I've never seen on any continent other than kunark. Yes, there are some evils that PvP but the other 50% hide in Kunark till there 60. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/urhainy.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rhainy</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/20/01 6:46:12 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=529.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sullen Zek</span><hr size=1> 50% Fudly? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Umm more like 90% heh. I can name every evil that PK's off the top of my head. When over 60% of the server pop is evil, that's saying something. They don't PK because they don't have to. Oh and because there's no one to PK...<br>
<br>
Actually with SoL alot of people will prolly make alts if they allow more than one char per account. Then rogues will have someone to lvl up with. And the 20% exp bonus and 50% less exp loss for death is really nice. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=cingin>Cingin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/20/01 10:52:03 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=529.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sullen Zek</span><hr size=1> RZ means you won't be the only newbie without any gear.  If you play on TZ or VZ, get ready to be killed daily by some twink with a Fungi, full blue diamond, and 2x the hp as you =P <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uaramistsz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>AramistSZ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/20/01 1:46:52 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=529.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Sullen Zek</span><hr size=1> Don't forget the 90% of newts that never leave Velious .....  If you go to SZ make a good aligned character, they need people!<br>
<br>
Aramist <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukevtheif.showPublicProfile?language=EN>KevTheif</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/21/01 6:42:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=529.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> re</span><hr size=1> vallon has a huge problem with 3teaming and twinking. most the lights cross team(called 3 teaming) and hide behind big bluebie light guilds.  the dark team has be destoryed by these 3teamers and they either moved to daoc, made a light twink or joined some 4team guild. the darks that are left are packed in howling stones, lower guk, and skyfire with occasional chardok control.<br>
 leveling will be hard in the early levels becuase of the huge amount of lightie twinks in fungi tunics. immy healing not much of a problem at least on vallon (unless your a lightie who refuses to 3 team, your a outcast in that case)becuase most everyone crossteams except the dark purist. there is only one  guild that has 4 teams and they dont grief or immy. <br>
<br>
thats how vallon is. if you want to be  a light then vallon prob the best server. if you want to grief and be on cr all day then go to sullon. otherwise go to Tallon or rallos hehe.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ugrimjawbadflagon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Grimjaw Badflagon</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/21/01 7:57:52 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=529.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re</span><hr size=1> Didnt you quit team good Aramist? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uwagorf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wagorf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/22/01 5:55:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=529.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Which PvP server is best ?</span><hr size=1> Tallon Zek Situation:<br>
<br>
1 Crossteaming Guild at the top. Since they are way up there shouldn't be a problem for you as a new player.<br>
<br>
Light team far outpowers/outnumbers dark team now. Most high level darks have joined the uber x-teaming guild (which is like 80% dark 20% light). <br>
<br>
Because of this situation, more and more people flock to the light team every day. <br>
